title: 20 min Full Body Dumbbell Workout | Build Muscle & Strength | Burn Fat 🔥
description:
Highly effective full body dumbbell workout at home. This resistance workout helps build muscle and strength using compound movements and a slow to moderate rep tempo. This training session targets the whole body including your legs (hamstrings, quadriceps and calves), glutes (glute minimus, glute medius and gluteus Maximus) it also targets your chest, arms (shoulders, biceps and triceps), back and core (abs). Burn body fat, burn calories and build muscle in just 20 minutes with this dumbbell full body strength workout.
This session is programmed to benefit all levels! Give this workout routine a go, and let me know how you did in the comments! 🔥

Thank you for providing us with enough time between exercises to get into the new position.  The 20 minute format is really working for me.  I prefer to work hard for 20 to 30 minutes than to drag the workout on for 40 minutes or so 👍.
Not gonna lie. I’m thinking, this will be a nice light warmup before my real workout. Nope. It kicked my butt. Incredible workout and minimal equipment.👍
